{"tid":990464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關愛共享計劃津貼, 斬咗幾多棵樹?","createTime":"2019-01-21T15:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T17:29:22.000Z","uid":16970,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2f2d9c21c43153a5c5d0143c50dbc293ffa67b","tid":990464,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://png.pngtree.com/thumb_back/fw800/photos/md/2017-09-06/lumber_trees_tree_trunks_wood.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpng.pngtree.com%2Fthumb_back%2Ffw800%2Fphotos%2Fmd%2F2017-09-06%2Flumber_trees_tree_trunks_wood.jpg&h=8d216dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據政府資料，大概有二百八十萬香港人有資格申領四千蚊關愛共享計劃津貼。申請表一式四頁，即係夾埋最少要印一千一百二十萬頁紙。<br />\n<br />\n每噸紙漿大約要斬廿四棵平均高十二米、樹幹直徑十五至二十厘米嘅樹木，然後每噸紙漿可以生產四十箱每箱五千張嘅嘅紙。要製造一千一百二十萬頁紙，就要五十六噸紙漿，即係要斬一千三百四十四棵樹。<br />\n<br />\n假設每棵樹樹冠六米，咁一千三百四十四棵樹就可以覆蓋到三點八公頃，即係九十個籃球場咁大。<br />\n<br />\n然後，政府同你講，冇得上網申請。真係好環保呀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1827715380801641/posts/2223854494521059/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1827715380801641%2Fposts%2F2223854494521059%2F&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4InzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ecb76da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1827715380801641/posts/2223854494521059/</a>"},{"pid":"7f8963ee679377d22ff7988f61d8fca69eab8dae","tid":990464,"uid":127727,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"召喚環保撚"},{"pid":"8acfe0b91000f5f99a23b0c8911f933775c74ea3","tid":990464,"uid":124156,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"環保撚呢？去咗邊啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd5b1615e455b5e9b7ab631c03d82d7df8baed5","tid":990464,"uid":19678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"推！where is 環保撚?"},{"pid":"c5c8482f5ba2179fb5f1882a2706169a4aa9a178","tid":990464,"uid":167330,"like":11,"dis